OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy today with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle. Rain
OL,7,Fwill turn heavier into the afternoon,
OL,8,Falthough it will still be mild across
OL,9,Fthe region for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRain and winds will ease a
OL,12,Flittle tonight, but it will remain
OL,13,Fcloudy and mild with outbreaks of
OL,14,Fdrizzle. Fog forming over the hills.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA spell of heavy rain and
OL,17,Fblustery winds will move through on
OL,18,FWednesday morning, followed by drier
OL,19,Fand brighter weather. Feeling warm in
OL,20,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
